imdb.plot outline: The story of two lovers: Antonio and Camila, who are cousins and have grown together, playing with each other's life and love. They became lovers, who find passion and love, as two feelings that can provide them with lots of adventures and bets, never to be taken seriously. This time, Camila decides to go a little further on her bet with Antonio and challenges him to sleep with Sofía, a beautiful, young, sincere woman, who immediately falls in love with handsome Antonio. Disregarding any respect for her feelings, Antonio then decides that he must also marry her and control her, but never admitting to Camila, his real feelings for Sofía.
imdb.title: Perro Amor
plot: The story of two lovers: Antonio and Camila, who are cousins and have grown together, playing with each other's life and love. They became lovers, who find passion and love, as two feelings that can provide them with lots of adventures and bets, never to be taken seriously. This time, Camila decides to go a little further on her bet with Antonio and challenges him to sleep with Sofía, a beautiful, young, sincere woman, who immediately falls in love with handsome Antonio. Disregarding any respect for her feelings, Antonio then decides that he must also marry her and control her, but never admitting to Camila, his real feelings for Sofía.::Erika Henao
